         <th aria-label="Batting Average" data-stat="batting_avg" class=" hide_non_quals center" data-tip="&lt;strong&gt;Hits/At Bats&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;For recent years, leaders need 3.1 PA&lt;br&gt;per team game played&lt;br&gt;Bold indicates highest BA using current stats&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;all_time_record&quot;&gt;Gold&lt;/span&gt; means awarded title at end of year." data-filter="1" data-name="Batting Average" >BA</th>
         <th aria-label="On-Base%" data-stat="onbase_perc" class=" hide_non_quals center" data-tip="&lt;strong&gt;(H + BB + HBP)/(At Bats + BB + HBP + SF)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;For recent years, leaders need 3.1 PA&lt;br&gt;per team game played" data-filter="1" data-name="On-Base%" >OBP</th>
         <th aria-label="Slugging %" data-stat="slugging_perc" class=" hide_non_quals center" data-tip="<strong>Total Bases/At Bats or <br>(1B + 2*2B + 3*3B + 4*HR)/AB</strong><br>For recent years, leaders need 3.1 PA<br>per team game played" data-filter="1" data-name="Slugging %" >SLG</th>
         <th aria-label="On-Base Plus Slugging" data-stat="onbase_plus_slugging" class=" hide_non_quals center" data-tip="&lt;strong&gt;On-Base + Slugging Percentages &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;For recent years, leaders need 3.1 PA&lt;br&gt;per team game played" data-filter="1" data-name="On-Base Plus Slugging" >OPS</th>
         <th aria-label="Adjusted OPS+" data-stat="onbase_plus_slugging_plus" class=" hide_non_quals center" data-tip="&lt;strong&gt;OPS+&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;100*[OBP/lg OBP + SLG/lg SLG - 1]&lt;br&gt;Adjusted to the player&amp;#x2019;s ballpark(s)" >OPS+</th>
         <th aria-label="Total Bases" data-stat="TB" class=" center" data-tip="&lt;strong&gt;Total Bases&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Singles + 2 x Doubles + 3 x Triples + 4 x Home Runs." >TB</th>
         <th aria-label="Double Plays Grounded Into" data-stat="GIDP" class=" center" data-tip="&lt;strong&gt;Double Plays Grounded Into&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Only includes standard 6-4-3, 4-3, etc. double plays.&lt;br&gt;First tracked in 1933.&lt;br&gt;For gamelogs only in seasons we have play-by-play, we include triple plays as well.&lt;br&gt;All official seasonal totals do not include GITP&#39;s." >GDP</th>
         <th aria-label="Hit By Pitch" data-stat="HBP" class=" center" data-tip="Times Hit by a Pitch." >HBP</th>
         <th aria-label="Sacrifice Hits" data-stat="SH" class=" center" data-tip="Sacrifice Hits (Sacrifice Bunts)" >SH</th>
         <th aria-label="Sacrifice Flies" data-stat="SF" class=" center" data-tip="<strong>Sacrifice Flies</strong><br>First tracked in 1954." >SF</th>
         <th aria-label="Intentional Bases on Balls" data-stat="IBB" class=" center" data-tip="&lt;strong&gt;Intentional Bases on Balls&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;First tracked in 1955." >IBB</th>
         <th aria-label=" Positions Played The positions either followed by the games played at that position or in order of games or innings played. For a single season, * indicates they played at least 2/3rds of the team games there Positions after / indicate less than ten games played at those positions. For career, a + sign means more than 300 games at that position and a - sign means less than 30 games." data-stat="pos_summary" class=" sort_default_asc left" data-tip="&lt;strong&gt;Positions Played&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;The positions either followed by the games played at that position&lt;br&gt; or in order of games or innings played.&lt;br&gt;For a single season, &lt;strong&gt;*&lt;/strong&gt; indicates they played at least 2/3rds of the team games there&lt;br&gt;Positions after &lt;/strong&gt;/&lt;/strong&gt; indicate less than ten games played at those positions.&lt;br&gt;For career, a + sign means more than 300 games at that position and&lt;br&gt;a - sign means less than 30 games." >Pos&nbsp;Summary</th>
      </tr>

         <th aria-label="Player&#x2019;s age at midnight of June 30th of that year" data-stat="age" class=" sort_default_asc show_partial_when_sorting center" data-tip="Player&#x2019;s age at midnight of June 30th of that year" >Age</th>
         <th aria-label="Tm" data-stat="team_ID" class=" sort_default_asc show_partial_when_sorting center" >Tm</th>
         <th aria-label=" League AL - American League (1901-present) NL - National League (1876-present) AA - American Association (1882-1891) UA - Union Association (1884) PL - Players League (1890) FL - Federal League (1914-1915) NA - National Association (1871-1875)" data-stat="lg_ID" class=" sort_default_asc center" data-tip="&lt;strong&gt;League&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AL&lt;/strong&gt; - American League (1901-present)&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;NL&lt;/strong&gt; - National League (1876-present)&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AA&lt;/strong&gt; - American Association (1882-1891)&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;UA&lt;/strong&gt; - Union Association (1884)&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PL&lt;/strong&gt; - Players League (1890)&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FL&lt;/strong&gt; - Federal League (1914-1915)&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;NA&lt;/strong&gt; - National Association (1871-1875)" >Lg</th>
         <th aria-label="Games Played" data-stat="G" class=" center" data-tip="<b>Games Played</b><br>This includes all times that the player appeared on the lineup card. Pitchers in non-DH games that appeared on the lineup card but didn't bat will still have a game in this column." >G</th>
         <th aria-label="Plate Appearances" data-stat="PA" class=" center" data-tip="&lt;strong&gt;Plate Appearances&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;When available, we use actual plate appearances from play-by-play game accounts&lt;br&gt;Otherwise estimated using AB + BB + HBP + SF + SH,&lt;br&gt;which excludes catcher interferences.&lt;br&gt;When &lt;span class=tooltip&gt;this color&lt;/span&gt; click for a summary of each PA." >PA</th>
         <th aria-label="At Bats" data-stat="AB" class=" center" data-tip="At Bats" >AB</th>
         <th aria-label="Runs Scored" data-stat="R" class=" center" data-tip="Runs Scored/Allowed" >R</th>
         <th aria-label="Hits" data-stat="H" class=" center" data-tip="Hits/Hits Allowed" >H</th>
         <th aria-label="Doubles" data-stat="2B" class=" center" data-tip="Doubles Hit/Allowed" >2B</th>
         <th aria-label="Triples" data-stat="3B" class=" center" data-tip="Triples Hit/Allowed" >3B</th>
         <th aria-label="Home Runs" data-stat="HR" class=" center" data-tip="Home Runs Hit/Allowed" >HR</th>
         <th aria-label="Runs Batted In" data-stat="RBI" class=" center" data-tip="Runs Batted In" >RBI</th>
         <th aria-label="Stolen Bases" data-stat="SB" class=" center" data-tip="Stolen Bases" >SB</th>
         <th aria-label="Caught Stealing" data-stat="CS" class=" center" data-tip="Caught Stealing" >CS</th>
         <th aria-label="Bases on Balls" data-stat="BB" class=" center" data-tip="Bases on Balls/Walks" >BB</th>
         <th aria-label="Strikeouts" data-stat="SO" class=" center" data-tip="Strikeouts" >SO</th>
         <th aria-label="Batting Average" data-stat="batting_avg" class=" hide_non_quals center" data-tip="&lt;strong&gt;Hits/At Bats&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;For recent years, leaders need 3.1 PA&lt;br&gt;per team game played&lt;br&gt;Bold indicates highest BA using current stats&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;all_time_record&quot;&gt;Gold&lt;/span&gt; means awarded title at end of year." data-filter="1" data-name="Batting Average" >BA</th>
         <th aria-label="On-Base%" data-stat="onbase_perc" class=" hide_non_quals center" data-tip="&lt;strong&gt;(H + BB + HBP)/(At Bats + BB + HBP + SF)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;For recent years, leaders need 3.1 PA&lt;br&gt;per team game played" data-filter="1" data-name="On-Base%" >OBP</th>
         <th aria-label="Slugging %" data-stat="slugging_perc" class=" hide_non_quals center" data-tip="<strong>Total Bases/At Bats or <br>(1B + 2*2B + 3*3B + 4*HR)/AB</strong><br>For recent years, leaders need 3.1 PA<br>per team game played" data-filter="1" data-name="Slugging %" >SLG</th>
         <th aria-label="On-Base Plus Slugging" data-stat="onbase_plus_slugging" class=" hide_non_quals center" data-tip="&lt;strong&gt;On-Base + Slugging Percentages &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;For recent years, leaders need 3.1 PA&lt;br&gt;per team game played" data-filter="1" data-name="On-Base Plus Slugging" >OPS</th>
         <th aria-label="Adjusted OPS+" data-stat="onbase_plus_slugging_plus" class=" hide_non_quals center" data-tip="&lt;strong&gt;OPS+&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;100*[OBP/lg OBP + SLG/lg SLG - 1]&lt;br&gt;Adjusted to the player&amp;#x2019;s ballpark(s)" >OPS+</th>
         <th aria-label="Total Bases" data-stat="TB" class=" center" data-tip="&lt;strong&gt;Total Bases&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Singles + 2 x Doubles + 3 x Triples + 4 x Home Runs." >TB</th>
         <th aria-label="Double Plays Grounded Into" data-stat="GIDP" class=" center" data-tip="&lt;strong&gt;Double Plays Grounded Into&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Only includes standard 6-4-3, 4-3, etc. double plays.&lt;br&gt;First tracked in 1933.&lt;br&gt;For gamelogs only in seasons we have play-by-play, we include triple plays as well.&lt;br&gt;All official seasonal totals do not include GITP&#39;s." >GDP</th>
         <th aria-label="Hit By Pitch" data-stat="HBP" class=" center" data-tip="Times Hit by a Pitch." >HBP</th>
         <th aria-label="Sacrifice Hits" data-stat="SH" class=" center" data-tip="Sacrifice Hits (Sacrifice Bunts)" >SH</th>
         <th aria-label="Sacrifice Flies" data-stat="SF" class=" center" data-tip="<strong>Sacrifice Flies</strong><br>First tracked in 1954." >SF</th>
         <th aria-label="Intentional Bases on Balls" data-stat="IBB" class=" center" data-tip="&lt;strong&gt;Intentional Bases on Balls&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;First tracked in 1955." >IBB</th>
         <th aria-label=" Positions Played The positions either followed by the games played at that position or in order of games or innings played. For a single season, * indicates they played at least 2/3rds of the team games there Positions after / indicate less than ten games played at those positions. For career, a + sign means more than 300 games at that position and a - sign means less than 30 games." data-stat="pos_summary" class=" sort_default_asc left" data-tip="&lt;strong&gt;Positions Played&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;The positions either followed by the games played at that position&lt;br&gt; or in order of games or innings played.&lt;br&gt;For a single season, &lt;strong&gt;*&lt;/strong&gt; indicates they played at least 2/3rds of the team games there&lt;br&gt;Positions after &lt;/strong&gt;/&lt;/strong&gt; indicate less than ten games played at those positions.&lt;br&gt;For career, a + sign means more than 300 games at that position and&lt;br&gt;a - sign means less than 30 games." >Pos&nbsp;Summary</th>
      </tr>

         <th aria-label="Sacrifice Hits" data-stat="SH" class=" center" data-tip="Sacrifice Hits (Sacrifice Bunts)" >SH</th>

         <th aria-label=" Positions Played The positions either followed by the games played at that position or in order of games or innings played. For a single season, * indicates they played at least 2/3rds of the team games there Positions after / indicate less than ten games played at those positions. For career, a + sign means more than 300 games at that position and a - sign means less than 30 games." data-stat="pos_summary" class=" sort_default_asc left" data-tip="&lt;strong&gt;Positions Played&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;The positions either followed by the games played at that position&lt;br&gt; or in order of games or innings played.&lt;br&gt;For a single season, &lt;strong&gt;*&lt;/strong&gt; indicates they played at least 2/3rds of the team games there&lt;br&gt;Positions after &lt;/strong&gt;/&lt;/strong&gt; indicate less than ten games played at those positions.&lt;br&gt;For career, a + sign means more than 300 games at that position and&lt;br&gt;a - sign means less than 30 games." >Pos&nbsp;Summary</th>
      </tr>

         <th aria-label="Player&#x2019;s age at midnight of June 30th of that year" data-stat="age" class=" sort_default_asc show_partial_when_sorting center" data-tip="Player&#x2019;s age at midnight of June 30th of that year" >Age</th>

         <th aria-label=" League AL - American League (1901-present) NL - National League (1876-present) AA - American Association (1882-1891) UA - Union Association (1884) PL - Players League (1890) FL - Federal League (1914-1915) NA - National Association (1871-1875)" data-stat="lg_ID" class=" sort_default_asc center" data-tip="&lt;strong&gt;League&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AL&lt;/strong&gt; - American League (1901-present)&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;NL&lt;/strong&gt; - National League (1876-present)&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AA&lt;/strong&gt; - American Association (1882-1891)&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;UA&lt;/strong&gt; - Union Association (1884)&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PL&lt;/strong&gt; - Players League (1890)&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FL&lt;/strong&gt; - Federal League (1914-1915)&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;NA&lt;/strong&gt; - National Association (1871-1875)" >Lg</th>
         <th aria-label="Games Played" data-stat="G" class=" center" data-tip="<b>Games Played</b><br>This includes all times that the player appeared on the lineup card. Pitchers in non-DH games that appeared on the lineup card but didn't bat will still have a game in this column." >G</th>
         <th aria-label="Plate Appearances" data-stat="PA" class=" center" data-tip="&lt;strong&gt;Plate Appearances&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;When available, we use actual plate appearances from play-by-play game accounts&lt;br&gt;Otherwise estimated using AB + BB + HBP + SF + SH,&lt;br&gt;which excludes catcher interferences.&lt;br&gt;When &lt;span class=tooltip&gt;this color&lt;/span&gt; click for a summary of each PA." >PA</th>
         <th aria-label="At Bats" data-stat="AB" class=" center" data-tip="At Bats" >AB</th>
         <th aria-label="Runs Scored" data-stat="R" class=" center" data-tip="Runs Scored/Allowed" >R</th>
         <th aria-label="Hits" data-stat="H" class=" center" data-tip="Hits/Hits Allowed" >H</th>
         <th aria-label="Doubles" data-stat="2B" class=" center" data-tip="Doubles Hit/Allowed" >2B</th>
         <th aria-label="Triples" data-stat="3B" class=" center" data-tip="Triples Hit/Allowed" >3B</th>
         <th aria-label="Home Runs" data-stat="HR" class=" center" data-tip="Home Runs Hit/Allowed" >HR</th>
         <th aria-label="Runs Batted In" data-stat="RBI" class=" center" data-tip="Runs Batted In" >RBI</th>
         <th aria-label="Stolen Bases" data-stat="SB" class=" center" data-tip="Stolen Bases" >SB</th>
         <th aria-label="Caught Stealing" data-stat="CS" class=" center" data-tip="Caught Stealing" >CS</th>
         <th aria-label="Bases on Balls" data-stat="BB" class=" center" data-tip="Bases on Balls/Walks" >BB</th>
         <th aria-label="Strikeouts" data-stat="SO" class=" center" data-tip="Strikeouts" >SO</th>
         <th aria-label="Batting Average" data-stat="batting_avg" class=" hide_non_quals center" data-tip="&lt;strong&gt;Hits/At Bats&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;For recent years, leaders need 3.1 PA&lt;br&gt;per team game played&lt;br&gt;Bold indicates highest BA using current stats&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;all_time_record&quot;&gt;Gold&lt;/span&gt; means awarded title at end of year." data-filter="1" data-name="Batting Average" >BA</th>
         <th aria-label="On-Base%" data-stat="onbase_perc" class=" hide_non_quals center" data-tip="&lt;strong&gt;(H + BB + HBP)/(At Bats + BB + HBP + SF)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;For recent years, leaders need 3.1 PA&lt;br&gt;per team game played" data-filter="1" data-name="On-Base%" >OBP</th>
         <th aria-label="Slugging %" data-stat="slugging_perc" class=" hide_non_quals center" data-tip="<strong>Total Bases/At Bats or <br>(1B + 2*2B + 3*3B + 4*HR)/AB</strong><br>For recent years, leaders need 3.1 PA<br>per team game played" data-filter="1" data-name="Slugging %" >SLG</th>
         <th aria-label="On-Base Plus Slugging" data-stat="onbase_plus_slugging" class=" hide_non_quals center" data-tip="&lt;strong&gt;On-Base + Slugging Percentages &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;For recent years, leaders need 3.1 PA&lt;br&gt;per team game played" data-filter="1" data-name="On-Base Plus Slugging" >OPS</th>
         <th aria-label="Adjusted OPS+" data-stat="onbase_plus_slugging_plus" class=" hide_non_quals center" data-tip="&lt;strong&gt;OPS+&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;100*[OBP/lg OBP + SLG/lg SLG - 1]&lt;br&gt;Adjusted to the player&amp;#x2019;s ballpark(s)" >OPS+</th>
         <th aria-label="Total Bases" data-stat="TB" class=" center" data-tip="&lt;strong&gt;Total Bases&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Singles + 2 x Doubles + 3 x Triples + 4 x Home Runs." >TB</th>
         <th aria-label="Double Plays Grounded Into" data-stat="GIDP" class=" center" data-tip="&lt;strong&gt;Double Plays Grounded Into&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Only includes standard 6-4-3, 4-3, etc. double plays.&lt;br&gt;First tracked in 1933.&lt;br&gt;For gamelogs only in seasons we have play-by-play, we include triple plays as well.&lt;br&gt;All official seasonal totals do not include GITP&#39;s." >GDP</th>
         <th aria-label="Hit By Pitch" data-stat="HBP" class=" center" data-tip="Times Hit by a Pitch." >HBP</th>
         <th aria-label="Sacrifice Hits" data-stat="SH" class=" center" data-tip="Sacrifice Hits (Sacrifice Bunts)" >SH</th>
         <th aria-label="Sacrifice Flies" data-stat="SF" class=" center" data-tip="<strong>Sacrifice Flies</strong><br>First tracked in 1954." >SF</th>
         <th aria-label="Intentional Bases on Balls" data-stat="IBB" class=" center" data-tip="&lt;strong&gt;Intentional Bases on Balls&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;First tracked in 1955." >IBB</th>
         <th aria-label=" Positions Played The positions either followed by the games played at that position or in order of games or innings played. For a single season, * indicates they played at least 2/3rds of the team games there Positions after / indicate less than ten games played at those positions. For career, a + sign means more than 300 games at that position and a - sign means less than 30 games." data-stat="pos_summary" class=" sort_default_asc left" data-tip="&lt;strong&gt;Positions Played&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;The positions either followed by the games played at that position&lt;br&gt; or in order of games or innings played.&lt;br&gt;For a single season, &lt;strong&gt;*&lt;/strong&gt; indicates they played at least 2/3rds of the team games there&lt;br&gt;Positions after &lt;/strong&gt;/&lt;/strong&gt; indicate less than ten games played at those positions.&lt;br&gt;For career, a + sign means more than 300 games at that position and&lt;br&gt;a - sign means less than 30 games." >Pos&nbsp;Summary</th>
      </tr>

         <th aria-label="Double Plays Grounded Into" data-stat="GIDP" class=" center" data-tip="&lt;strong&gt;Double Plays Grounded Into&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Only includes standard 6-4-3, 4-3, etc. double plays.&lt;br&gt;First tracked in 1933.&lt;br&gt;For gamelogs only in seasons we have play-by-play, we include triple plays as well.&lt;br&gt;All official seasonal totals do not include GITP&#39;s." >GDP</th>
         <th aria-label="Hit By Pitch" data-stat="HBP" class=" center" data-tip="Times Hit by a Pitch." >HBP</th>
         <th aria-label="Sacrifice Hits" data-stat="SH" class=" center" data-tip="Sacrifice Hits (Sacrifice Bunts)" >SH</th>
         <th aria-label="Sacrifice Flies" data-stat="SF" class=" center" data-tip="<strong>Sacrifice Flies</strong><br>First tracked in 1954." >SF</th>
         <th aria-label="Intentional Bases on Balls" data-stat="IBB" class=" center" data-tip="&lt;strong&gt;Intentional Bases on Balls&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;First tracked in 1955." >IBB</th>
         <th aria-label=" Positions Played The positions either followed by the games played at that position or in order of games or innings played. For a single season, * indicates they played at least 2/3rds of the team games there Positions after / indicate less than ten games played at those positions. For career, a + sign means more than 300 games at that position and a - sign means less than 30 games." data-stat="pos_summary" class=" sort_default_asc left" data-tip="&lt;strong&gt;Positions Played&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;The positions either followed by the games played at that position&lt;br&gt; or in order of games or innings played.&lt;br&gt;For a single season, &lt;strong&gt;*&lt;/strong&gt; indicates they played at least 2/3rds of the team games there&lt;br&gt;Positions after &lt;/strong&gt;/&lt;/strong&gt; indicate less than ten games played at those positions.&lt;br&gt;For career, a + sign means more than 300 games at that position and&lt;br&gt;a - sign means less than 30 games." >Pos&nbsp;Summary</th>
      </tr>

         <th aria-label="Player&#x2019;s age at midnight of June 30th of that year" data-stat="age" class=" sort_default_asc show_partial_when_sorting center" data-tip="Player&#x2019;s age at midnight of June 30th of that year" >Age</th>

         <th aria-label=" League AL - American League (1901-present) NL - National League (1876-present) AA - American Association (1882-1891) UA - Union Association (1884) PL - Players League (1890) FL - Federal League (1914-1915) NA - National Association (1871-1875)" data-stat="lg_ID" class=" sort_default_asc center" data-tip="&lt;strong&gt;League&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AL&lt;/strong&gt; - American League (1901-present)&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;NL&lt;/strong&gt; - National League (1876-present)&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AA&lt;/strong&gt; - American Association (1882-1891)&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;UA&lt;/strong&gt; - Union Association (1884)&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PL&lt;/strong&gt; - Players League (1890)&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FL&lt;/strong&gt; - Federal League (1914-1915)&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;NA&lt;/strong&gt; - National Association (1871-1875)" >Lg</th>
         <th aria-label="Games Played" data-stat="G" class=" center" data-tip="<b>Games Played</b><br>This includes all times that the player appeared on the lineup card. Pitchers in non-DH games that appeared on the lineup card but didn't bat will still have a game in this column." >G</th>
         <th aria-label="Plate Appearances" data-stat="PA" class=" center" data-tip="&lt;strong&gt;Plate Appearances&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;When available, we use actual plate appearances from play-by-play game accounts&lt;br&gt;Otherwise estimated using AB + BB + HBP + SF + SH,&lt;br&gt;which excludes catcher interferences.&lt;br&gt;When &lt;span class=tooltip&gt;this color&lt;/span&gt; click for a summary of each PA." >PA</th>
         <th aria-label="At Bats" data-stat="AB" class=" center" data-tip="At Bats" >AB</th>
         <th aria-label="Runs Scored" data-stat="R" class=" center" data-tip="Runs Scored/Allowed" >R</th>
         <th aria-label="Hits" data-stat="H" class=" center" data-tip="Hits/Hits Allowed" >H</th>
         <th aria-label="Doubles" data-stat="2B" class=" center" data-tip="Doubles Hit/Allowed" >2B</th>
         <th aria-label="Triples" data-stat="3B" class=" center" data-tip="Triples Hit/Allowed" >3B</th>
         <th aria-label="Home Runs" data-stat="HR" class=" center" data-tip="Home Runs Hit/Allowed" >HR</th>
         <th aria-label="Runs Batted In" data-stat="RBI" class=" center" data-tip="Runs Batted In" >RBI</th>
         <th aria-label="Stolen Bases" data-stat="SB" class=" center" data-tip="Stolen Bases" >SB</th>
         <th aria-label="Caught Stealing" data-stat="CS" class=" center" data-tip="Caught Stealing" >CS</th>
         <th aria-label="Bases on Balls" data-stat="BB" class=" center" data-tip="Bases on Balls/Walks" >BB</th>
         <th aria-label="Strikeouts" data-stat="SO" class=" center" data-tip="Strikeouts" >SO</th>
         <th aria-label="Batting Average" data-stat="batting_avg" class=" hide_non_quals center" data-tip="&lt;strong&gt;Hits/At Bats&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;For recent years, leaders need 3.1 PA&lt;br&gt;per team game played&lt;br&gt;Bold indicates highest BA using current stats&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;all_time_record&quot;&gt;Gold&lt;/span&gt; means awarded title at end of year." data-filter="1" data-name="Batting Average" >BA</th>
         <th aria-label="On-Base%" data-stat="onbase_perc" class=" hide_non_quals center" data-tip="&lt;strong&gt;(H + BB + HBP)/(At Bats + BB + HBP + SF)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;For recent years, leaders need 3.1 PA&lt;br&gt;per team game played" data-filter="1" data-name="On-Base%" >OBP</th>
         <th aria-label="Slugging %" data-stat="slugging_perc" class=" hide_non_quals center" data-tip="<strong>Total Bases/At Bats or <br>(1B + 2*2B + 3*3B + 4*HR)/AB</strong><br>For recent years, leaders need 3.1 PA<br>per team game played" data-filter="1" data-name="Slugging %" >SLG</th>
         <th aria-label="On-Base Plus Slugging" data-stat="onbase_plus_slugging" class=" hide_non_quals center" data-tip="&lt;strong&gt;On-Base + Slugging Percentages &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;For recent years, leaders need 3.1 PA&lt;br&gt;per team game played" data-filter="1" data-name="On-Base Plus Slugging" >OPS</th>
         <th aria-label="Adjusted OPS+" data-stat="onbase_plus_slugging_plus" class=" hide_non_quals center" data-tip="&lt;strong&gt;OPS+&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;100*[OBP/lg OBP + SLG/lg SLG - 1]&lt;br&gt;Adjusted to the player&amp;#x2019;s ballpark(s)" >OPS+</th>
         <th aria-label="Total Bases" data-stat="TB" class=" center" data-tip="&lt;strong&gt;Total Bases&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Singles + 2 x Doubles + 3 x Triples + 4 x Home Runs." >TB</th>
         <th aria-label="Double Plays Grounded Into" data-stat="GIDP" class=" center" data-tip="&lt;strong&gt;Double Plays Grounded Into&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Only includes standard 6-4-3, 4-3, etc. double plays.&lt;br&gt;First tracked in 1933.&lt;br&gt;For gamelogs only in seasons we have play-by-play, we include triple plays as well.&lt;br&gt;All official seasonal totals do not include GITP&#39;s." >GDP</th>
         <th aria-label="Hit By Pitch" data-stat="HBP" class=" center" data-tip="Times Hit by a Pitch." >HBP</th>
         <th aria-label="Sacrifice Hits" data-stat="SH" class=" center" data-tip="Sacrifice Hits (Sacrifice Bunts)" >SH</th>
         <th aria-label="Sacrifice Flies" data-stat="SF" class=" center" data-tip="<strong>Sacrifice Flies</strong><br>First tracked in 1954." >SF</th>
         <th aria-label="Intentional Bases on Balls" data-stat="IBB" class=" center" data-tip="&lt;strong&gt;Intentional Bases on Balls&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;First tracked in 1955." >IBB</th>
         <th aria-label=" Positions Played The positions either followed by the games played at that position or in order of games or innings played. For a single season, * indicates they played at least 2/3rds of the team games there Positions after / indicate less than ten games played at those positions. For career, a + sign means more than 300 games at that position and a - sign means less than 30 games." data-stat="pos_summary" class=" sort_default_asc left" data-tip="&lt;strong&gt;Positions Played&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;The positions either followed by the games played at that position&lt;br&gt; or in order of games or innings played.&lt;br&gt;For a single season, &lt;strong&gt;*&lt;/strong&gt; indicates they played at least 2/3rds of the team games there&lt;br&gt;Positions after &lt;/strong&gt;/&lt;/strong&gt; indicate less than ten games played at those positions.&lt;br&gt;For career, a + sign means more than 300 games at that position and&lt;br&gt;a - sign means less than 30 games." >Pos&nbsp;Summary</th>

         <th aria-label="Hit By Pitch" data-stat="HBP" class=" center" data-tip="Times Hit by a Pitch." >HBP</th>
         <th aria-label="Sacrifice Hits" data-stat="SH" class=" center" data-tip="Sacrifice Hits (Sacrifice Bunts)" >SH</th>
         <th aria-label="Sacrifice Flies" data-stat="SF" class=" center" data-tip="<strong>Sacrifice Flies</strong><br>First tracked in 1954." >SF</th>

         <th aria-label=" Positions Played The positions either followed by the games played at that position or in order of games or innings played. For a single season, * indicates they played at least 2/3rds of the team games there Positions after / indicate less than ten games played at those positions. For career, a + sign means more than 300 games at that position and a - sign means less than 30 games." data-stat="pos_summary" class=" sort_default_asc left" data-tip="&lt;strong&gt;Positions Played&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;The positions either followed by the games played at that position&lt;br&gt; or in order of games or innings played.&lt;br&gt;For a single season, &lt;strong&gt;*&lt;/strong&gt; indicates they played at least 2/3rds of the team games there&lt;br&gt;Positions after &lt;/strong&gt;/&lt;/strong&gt; indicate less than ten games played at those positions.&lt;br&gt;For career, a + sign means more than 300 games at that position and&lt;br&gt;a - sign means less than 30 games." >Pos&nbsp;Summary</th>
      </tr>

         <th aria-label="Player&#x2019;s age at midnight of June 30th of that year" data-stat="age" class=" sort_default_asc show_partial_when_sorting center" data-tip="Player&#x2019;s age at midnight of June 30th of that year" >Age</th>
         <th aria-label="Tm" data-stat="team_ID" class=" sort_default_asc show_partial_when_sorting center" >Tm</th>
         <th aria-label=" League AL - American League (1901-present) NL - National League (1876-present) AA - American Association (1882-1891) UA - Union Association (1884) PL - Players League (1890) FL - Federal League (1914-1915) NA - National Association (1871-1875)" data-stat="lg_ID" class=" sort_default_asc center" data-tip="&lt;strong&gt;League&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AL&lt;/strong&gt; - American League (1901-present)&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;NL&lt;/strong&gt; - National League (1876-present)&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AA&lt;/strong&gt; - American Association (1882-1891)&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;UA&lt;/strong&gt; - Union Association (1884)&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PL&lt;/strong&gt; - Players League (1890)&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FL&lt;/strong&gt; - Federal League (1914-1915)&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;NA&lt;/strong&gt; - National Association (1871-1875)" >Lg</th>
         <th aria-label="Games Played" data-stat="G" class=" center" data-tip="<b>Games Played</b><br>This includes all times that the player appeared on the lineup card. Pitchers in non-DH games that appeared on the lineup card but didn't bat will still have a game in this column." >G</th>
         <th aria-label="Plate Appearances" data-stat="PA" class=" center" data-tip="&lt;strong&gt;Plate Appearances&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;When available, we use actual plate appearances from play-by-play game accounts&lt;br&gt;Otherwise estimated using AB + BB + HBP + SF + SH,&lt;br&gt;which excludes catcher interferences.&lt;br&gt;When &lt;span class=tooltip&gt;this color&lt;/span&gt; click for a summary of each PA." >PA</th>
         <th aria-label="At Bats" data-stat="AB" class=" center" data-tip="At Bats" >AB</th>
         <th aria-label="Runs Scored" data-stat="R" class=" center" data-tip="Runs Scored/Allowed" >R</th>
         <th aria-label="Hits" data-stat="H" class=" center" data-tip="Hits/Hits Allowed" >H</th>
         <th aria-label="Doubles" data-stat="2B" class=" center" data-tip="Doubles Hit/Allowed" >2B</th>
         <th aria-label="Triples" data-stat="3B" class=" center" data-tip="Triples Hit/Allowed" >3B</th>
         <th aria-label="Home Runs" data-stat="HR" class=" center" data-tip="Home Runs Hit/Allowed" >HR</th>
         <th aria-label="Runs Batted In" data-stat="RBI" class=" center" data-tip="Runs Batted In" >RBI</th>
         <th aria-label="Stolen Bases" data-stat="SB" class=" center" data-tip="Stolen Bases" >SB</th>
         <th aria-label="Caught Stealing" data-stat="CS" class=" center" data-tip="Caught Stealing" >CS</th>
         <th aria-label="Bases on Balls" data-stat="BB" class=" center" data-tip="Bases on Balls/Walks" >BB</th>
         <th aria-label="Strikeouts" data-stat="SO" class=" center" data-tip="Strikeouts" >SO</th>
         <th aria-label="Batting Average" data-stat="batting_avg" class=" hide_non_quals center" data-tip="&lt;strong&gt;Hits/At Bats&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;For recent years, leaders need 3.1 PA&lt;br&gt;per team game played&lt;br&gt;Bold indicates highest BA using current stats&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;all_time_record&quot;&gt;Gold&lt;/span&gt; means awarded title at end of year." data-filter="1" data-name="Batting Average" >BA</th>
         <th aria-label="On-Base%" data-stat="onbase_perc" class=" hide_non_quals center" data-tip="&lt;strong&gt;(H + BB + HBP)/(At Bats + BB + HBP + SF)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;For recent years, leaders need 3.1 PA&lt;br&gt;per team game played" data-filter="1" data-name="On-Base%" >OBP</th>
         <th aria-label="Slugging %" data-stat="slugging_perc" class=" hide_non_quals center" data-tip="<strong>Total Bases/At Bats or <br>(1B + 2*2B + 3*3B + 4*HR)/AB</strong><br>For recent years, leaders need 3.1 PA<br>per team game played" data-filter="1" data-name="Slugging %" >SLG</th>
         <th aria-label="On-Base Plus Slugging" data-stat="onbase_plus_slugging" class=" hide_non_quals center" data-tip="&lt;strong&gt;On-Base + Slugging Percentages &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;For recent years, leaders need 3.1 PA&lt;br&gt;per team game played" data-filter="1" data-name="On-Base Plus Slugging" >OPS</th>
         <th aria-label="Adjusted OPS+" data-stat="onbase_plus_slugging_plus" class=" hide_non_quals center" data-tip="&lt;strong&gt;OPS+&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;100*[OBP/lg OBP + SLG/lg SLG - 1]&lt;br&gt;Adjusted to the player&amp;#x2019;s ballpark(s)" >OPS+</th>
         <th aria-label="Total Bases" data-stat="TB" class=" center" data-tip="&lt;strong&gt;Total Bases&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Singles + 2 x Doubles + 3 x Triples + 4 x Home Runs." >TB</th>
         <th aria-label="Double Plays Grounded Into" data-stat="GIDP" class=" center" data-tip="&lt;strong&gt;Double Plays Grounded Into&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Only includes standard 6-4-3, 4-3, etc. double plays.&lt;br&gt;First tracked in 1933.&lt;br&gt;For gamelogs only in seasons we have play-by-play, we include triple plays as well.&lt;br&gt;All official seasonal totals do not include GITP&#39;s." >GDP</th>
         <th aria-label="Hit By Pitch" data-stat="HBP" class=" center" data-tip="Times Hit by a Pitch." >HBP</th>
         <th aria-label="Sacrifice Hits" data-stat="SH" class=" center" data-tip="Sacrifice Hits (Sacrifice Bunts)" >SH</th>
         <th aria-label="Sacrifice Flies" data-stat="SF" class=" center" data-tip="<strong>Sacrifice Flies</strong><br>First tracked in 1954." >SF</th>
         <th aria-label="Intentional Bases on Balls" data-stat="IBB" class=" center" data-tip="&lt;strong&gt;Intentional Bases on Balls&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;First tracked in 1955." >IBB</th>
         <th aria-label=" Positions Played The positions either followed by the games played at that position or in order of games or innings played. For a single season, * indicates they played at least 2/3rds of the team games there Positions after / indicate less than ten games played at those positions. For career, a + sign means more than 300 games at that position and a - sign means less than 30 games." data-stat="pos_summary" class=" sort_default_asc left" data-tip="&lt;strong&gt;Positions Played&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;The positions either followed by the games played at that position&lt;br&gt; or in order of games or innings played.&lt;br&gt;For a single season, &lt;strong&gt;*&lt;/strong&gt; indicates they played at least 2/3rds of the team games there&lt;br&gt;Positions after &lt;/strong&gt;/&lt;/strong&gt; indicate less than ten games played at those positions.&lt;br&gt;For career, a + sign means more than 300 games at that position and&lt;br&gt;a - sign means less than 30 games." >Pos&nbsp;Summary</th>
      </tr>

         <th aria-label="Sacrifice Hits" data-stat="SH" class=" center" data-tip="Sacrifice Hits (Sacrifice Bunts)" >SH</th>

         <th aria-label=" Positions Played The positions either followed by the games played at that position or in order of games or innings played. For a single season, * indicates they played at least 2/3rds of the team games there Positions after / indicate less than ten games played at those positions. For career, a + sign means more than 300 games at that position and a - sign means less than 30 games." data-stat="pos_summary" class=" sort_default_asc left" data-tip="&lt;strong&gt;Positions Played&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;The positions either followed by the games played at that position&lt;br&gt; or in order of games or innings played.&lt;br&gt;For a single season, &lt;strong&gt;*&lt;/strong&gt; indicates they played at least 2/3rds of the team games there&lt;br&gt;Positions after &lt;/strong&gt;/&lt;/strong&gt; indicate less than ten games played at those positions.&lt;br&gt;For career, a + sign means more than 300 games at that position and&lt;br&gt;a - sign means less than 30 games." >Pos&nbsp;Summary</th>
      </tr>
